BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: if application "Google Chrome" is running then	tell application "Google Chrome"		repeat with t in tabs of windows			tell t				if URL starts with "http://soundcloud.com/" or URL starts with "https://soundcloud.com/" then					return text 1 thru -11 of (title of t as text)				end if			end tell		end repeat	end tellend ifreturn ""

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: if application "Google Chrome" is running then	tell application "Google Chrome"		repeat with t in tabs of windows			tell t				if URL starts with "http://www.youtube.com/watch" or URL starts with "https://www.youtube.com/watch" then					return text 1 thru -11 of (title of t as text)				end if			end tell		end repeat	end tellend ifreturn ""
